No, no, no. Please listen carefully.

73
00:07:40,740 --> 00:07:42,710
I have very important official business.

74
00:07:42,710 --> 00:07:44,990
I need to meet your manager immediately.

75
00:07:45,870 --> 00:07:50,730
[You Jiehui, Staff Member of
the Municipal Cultural Heritage Bureau]

76
00:07:53,100 --> 00:07:53,540
Hello.

77
00:07:54,140 --> 00:07:55,530
You, this is Cheng Zhi.

78
00:07:56,770 --> 00:07:58,570
Chief Cheng, what's the matter?

79
00:07:58,670 --> 00:08:00,230
The National Cultural Heritage
Administration just called me.

80
00:08:00,230 --> 00:08:01,640
Six Western Han nude
black pottery figurines

81
00:08:01,640 --> 00:08:04,230
from Qinchuan have been
smuggled out of our country.

82
00:08:04,230 --> 00:08:06,200
They will be auctioned
at 12 o'clock at midnight.

83
00:08:06,200 --> 00:08:07,270
Embassy staff

84
00:08:07,290 --> 00:08:09,190
have already gone to
negotiate with the auction house.

85
00:08:09,190 --> 00:08:11,080
But I'm afraid they might
try to make things difficult.

86
00:08:11,080 --> 00:08:13,300
I'll fax you the auction
details right away.

87
00:08:13,300 --> 00:08:14,040
You need to hurry up

88
00:08:14,040 --> 00:08:15,870
and ask an expert in archaeology
of Qin and Han Dynasties

89
00:08:15,870 --> 00:08:17,520
to assist with the content work.

90
00:08:17,520 --> 00:08:18,600
Deputy Chief Wang
from the provincial bureau

91
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:20,040
will go with you to see the expert.

92
00:08:20,040 --> 00:08:20,600
Okay.

93
00:08:21,160 --> 00:08:22,690
I'll arrange it right away.

94
00:08:27,040 --> 00:08:29,690
These six black pottery figurines,

95
00:08:29,800 --> 00:08:33,150
No. 32 on the catalogue at the moment.

96
00:08:33,730 --> 00:08:37,039
We request you to
immediately cease the auction

97
00:08:37,070 --> 00:08:41,429
and return those six
illegal relics to the Chinese side.

98
00:08:41,830 --> 00:08:42,669
Illegal?

99
00:08:43,679 --> 00:08:45,310
Then please allow our legal director

100
00:08:45,310 --> 00:08:47,190
to explain the law to you.

101
00:08:47,440 --> 00:08:50,840
Before these six
nude black pottery figurines

102
00:08:51,180 --> 00:08:53,610
were consigned to our auction house,

103
00:08:53,640 --> 00:08:55,000
they were combined with

104
00:08:55,000 --> 00:09:01,000
the legal ownership certificates
and cultural relic appraisal documents.

105
00:09:01,160 --> 00:09:04,520
Since you claim that
the figurines were stolen,

106
00:09:04,880 --> 00:09:07,550
do you have the specific case details,

107
00:09:08,100 --> 00:09:08,950
legal documents,

108
00:09:08,950 --> 00:09:11,240
and evidence of illegal smuggling?

109
00:09:11,360 --> 00:09:13,470
The legal documents you mentioned

110
00:09:13,470 --> 00:09:15,990
will be provided to you

111
00:09:16,400 --> 00:09:19,060
once we have investigated
the case thoroughly.

112
00:09:19,360 --> 00:09:20,490
However, for now,

113
00:09:20,640 --> 00:09:23,360
I request you to suspend the auction.

114
00:09:25,180 --> 00:09:26,110
Guyue Customs

115
00:09:26,470 --> 00:09:28,120
intercepted 34 black pottery figurines

116
00:09:28,120 --> 00:09:30,160
that were about to be
smuggled out of our country.

117
00:09:30,160 --> 00:09:31,160
In the investigation, they found that

118
00:09:30,530 --> 00:09:33,200
[Deputy Chief Wang,
Provincial Cultural Heritage Bureau]

119
00:09:31,950 --> 00:09:34,610
six pieces had already
been transported abroad

120
00:09:34,960 --> 00:09:38,150
and appeared in
Winthrop's auction catalogue.

121
00:09:38,520 --> 00:09:39,760
Our Provincial Cultural Heritage Bureau

122
00:09:39,760 --> 00:09:42,520
has talked to the Provincial Public
Security Department about the situation.

123
00:09:42,520 --> 00:09:43,560
They'll immediately ask some people

124
00:09:43,560 --> 00:09:45,090
from the Qinchuan Public Security Bureau

125
00:09:45,090 --> 00:09:46,370
to go to the Guyue Customs

126
00:09:46,370 --> 00:09:48,900
and retrieve the 34
black pottery figurines.

127
00:09:56,730 --> 00:09:57,160
Hello?

128
00:10:00,680 --> 00:10:01,480
I understand.

129
00:10:02,330 --> 00:10:03,930
We're on our way to Yangling.

130
00:10:04,610 --> 00:10:07,520
We're going to meet with Professor Zan
from Qinbei University.

131
00:10:07,520 --> 00:10:09,450
We'll prepare the documents at once.

132
00:10:09,450 --> 00:10:09,780
Okay.

133
00:10:10,680 --> 00:10:11,130
Bye.

134
00:10:12,730 --> 00:10:13,530
What's wrong?

135
00:10:13,610 --> 00:10:15,740
The National Administration called me.

136
00:10:15,740 --> 00:10:18,680
They said the other party needed us
to prepare documents

137
00:10:18,680 --> 00:10:20,280
and answer three questions.

138
00:10:21,040 --> 00:10:24,250
Why do we say that the black pottery
figurines are from China?

139
00:10:24,250 --> 00:10:26,510
Why do we say that they're from Qinchuan?

140
00:10:26,800 --> 00:10:29,860
Why do we say that they're from
the Western Han Dynasty?

141
00:10:32,240 --> 00:10:33,500
Where did you get this?

142
00:10:34,450 --> 00:10:36,250
I went to a market in the village today.

143
00:10:35,700 --> 00:10:40,410
[Luo Qing, Intern
at Yangling Archeology Base]

144
00:10:37,920 --> 00:10:39,380
Mr. Zan had just left,

145
00:10:39,560 --> 00:10:40,520
and you immediately went to the market?

146
00:10:40,520 --> 00:10:40,940
What?

147
00:10:41,120 --> 00:10:46,750
[Guo Shilin, Intern
at Yangling Archeology Base]

148
00:10:42,160 --> 00:10:43,900
Can't I relax a bit
after finishing my work?

149
00:10:43,900 --> 00:10:45,560
Besides, I went to the village

150
00:10:45,560 --> 00:10:47,490
to see what local people eat and drink

151
00:10:47,490 --> 00:10:49,880
and to check on things
like vegetables and grains.

152
00:10:49,880 --> 00:10:50,620
Guo Shilin

153
00:10:50,640 --> 00:10:52,070
usually ranks last in our class.

154
00:10:51,030 --> 00:10:56,160
[Fang Kun, Intern
at Yangling Archeology Base]

155
00:10:53,160 --> 00:10:54,960
But when it comes to loving life,

156
00:10:55,680 --> 00:10:56,540
he ranks first.

157
00:10:56,610 --> 00:10:57,940
Actually, archaeology

158
00:10:58,040 --> 00:10:58,920
is also a

159
00:10:59,560 --> 00:11:01,370
science of loving life, isn't it?

160
00:11:01,370 --> 00:11:02,160
What we study is all about

161
00:11:02,160 --> 00:11:03,880
what ancient people ate,
drank, and threw away.

162
00:11:03,880 --> 00:11:04,330
Right?

163
00:11:04,330 --> 00:11:05,060
That's true.

164
00:11:05,730 --> 00:11:07,210
With your description, our abstruse

165
00:11:07,210 --> 00:11:08,540
and complex profession

166
00:11:08,920 --> 00:11:11,490
sounds quite endearing and lovely.

167
00:11:12,040 --> 00:11:13,250
By the way, Luo Qing...

168
00:11:13,250 --> 00:11:14,370
After graduation, you want to join

169
00:11:14,370 --> 00:11:15,730
the Archaeology Institute of
the Social Sciences Academy, huh?

170
00:11:15,730 --> 00:11:17,520
Why do you have to join that institute?

171
00:11:17,520 --> 00:11:18,680
Let's just stay in Qinchuan,

172
00:11:18,680 --> 00:11:20,400
which was the ancient
capital of 13 dynasties.

173
00:11:20,400 --> 00:11:22,250
Where else could you engage in
archaeology except for Qinchuan?

174
00:11:22,250 --> 00:11:23,800
Luo Qing is from Beijing.

175
00:11:24,090 --> 00:11:25,130
She's a girl,

176
00:11:25,200 --> 00:11:27,130
