179
00:11:29,800 --> 00:11:31,680
At worst, you can marry
a man from Qinchuan.

180
00:11:31,680 --> 00:11:32,640
I'm single anyway.

181
00:11:32,640 --> 00:11:34,280
If you want a life partner, I'm available.

182
00:11:34,280 --> 00:11:35,920
How can you be so shameless?

183
00:11:35,920 --> 00:11:37,010
Who would want to marry...

184
00:11:37,010 --> 00:11:37,760
I mind.

185
00:11:37,780 --> 00:11:40,380
-Well...
-Luo Qing doesn't lack suitors here.

186
00:11:40,410 --> 00:11:42,370
There was a man who gave her
flowers a couple of days ago.

187
00:11:42,370 --> 00:11:43,730
He's from the Provincial
Identification Center.

188
00:11:43,730 --> 00:11:45,210
And he graduated from Peking University.

189
00:11:45,210 --> 00:11:46,400
Why are you such a gossiper?

190
00:11:46,400 --> 00:11:47,610
So what if he's from
the Provincial Identification Center?

191
00:11:47,610 --> 00:11:48,400
So what if he graduated
from Peking University?

192
00:11:48,400 --> 00:11:50,560
