193
00:11:50,560 --> 00:11:52,330
Have you heard of the saying
"First come, first served?"

194
00:11:52,330 --> 00:11:53,610
I'm going to interfere right away.

195
00:11:53,610 --> 00:11:54,250
Are you going to act recklessly?

196
00:11:54,250 --> 00:11:55,130
What are you going to do?

197
00:11:55,130 --> 00:11:56,090
Y-You'd better run away. Let me tell you.

198
00:11:56,090 --> 00:11:57,330
Can't you understand what I mean?

199
00:11:57,330 --> 00:11:58,250
What I mean is...

200
00:11:58,250 --> 00:12:00,250
