231
00:13:10,610 --> 00:13:11,640
I'd like to ask whether

232
00:13:11,640 --> 00:13:15,170
Professor Zan Maochang from
Qinbei University has checked in.

233
00:13:17,510 --> 00:13:18,440
Okay. Thank you.

234
00:13:19,850 --> 00:13:20,330
No?

235
00:13:22,330 --> 00:13:24,130
Mr. Zan took a flight tonight.

236
00:13:24,440 --> 00:13:26,920
