and hasn't landed yet?

237
00:13:26,920 --> 00:13:28,580
At your archaeological site,

238
00:13:28,730 --> 00:13:31,130
are there any other experts or professors?

239
00:13:31,290 --> 00:13:32,040
Here's the thing.

240
00:13:32,040 --> 00:13:32,760
Recently in Beijing, hasn't there

241
00:13:32,760 --> 00:13:35,280
