258
00:14:16,240 --> 00:14:16,640
Hello?

259
00:14:16,920 --> 00:14:17,340
Hello?

260
00:14:17,850 --> 00:14:18,490
Mr. Zan.

261
00:14:23,410 --> 00:14:23,990
Sir.

262
00:14:25,160 --> 00:14:27,450
