264
00:14:29,130 --> 00:14:32,880
before the auction of
those six black pottery figurines.

265
00:14:33,160 --> 00:14:34,740
Chief Wang, Mr. You.

266
00:14:34,850 --> 00:14:37,110
Those three students are all excellent.

267
00:14:37,370 --> 00:14:39,570
