1,000 yuan each.

540
00:26:19,080 --> 00:26:19,650
600 yuan.

541
00:26:21,870 --> 00:26:23,670
The price is 600 yuan as you said.

542
00:26:24,950 --> 00:26:26,060
You agreed so quickly?

543
00:26:26,060 --> 00:26:27,780
I came here with sincerity.

544
00:26:27,950 --> 00:26:30,210
I just trust your reputation as King Hua.

545
00:26:36,080 --> 00:26:36,800
But...

546
00:26:37,930 --> 00:26:39,080
I can only buy

547
00:26:40,320 --> 00:26:41,040
100 pieces.

548
00:26:41,280 --> 00:26:42,040
100 pieces?

549
00:26:42,650 --> 00:26:43,080
Yes.

550
00:26:44,890 --> 00:26:46,550
If you don't agree, it's fine.

551
00:26:46,700 --> 00:26:48,160
You can find someone else.

552
00:26:48,910 --> 00:26:49,690
No problem.

553
00:26:50,850 --> 00:26:53,450
The quality of the goods
isn't for me to decide.

554
00:26:54,070 --> 00:26:56,940
Just see how the market
responds to the 100 pieces.

555
00:26:57,730 --> 00:26:59,940
If it works out, there will be
more opportunities.

556
00:26:59,940 --> 00:27:01,200
If it doesn't work out,

557
00:27:02,150 --> 00:27:03,980
I'll owe you a favor.

558
00:27:04,890 --> 00:27:07,020
I'll wait for your news about the rest.

559
00:27:07,210 --> 00:27:09,360
Even if others want them, I won't sell.

560
00:27:13,600 --> 00:27:14,080
Okay.

561
00:27:15,780 --> 00:27:17,990
I think Zan is deliberately
giving us a hard time.

562
00:27:15,810 --> 00:27:20,550
[Yangling Archeology Base]

563
00:27:18,690 --> 00:27:20,360
Drawing artefact illustrations
and tidying up rooms

564
00:27:20,360 --> 00:27:22,360
are just tasks for undergraduates.

565
00:27:22,410 --> 00:27:24,290
Why did he ask graduate students
to waste time on these things?

566
00:27:24,290 --> 00:27:25,880
This is not a waste of time.

567
00:27:26,280 --> 00:27:27,360
Undergraduate education is meant to be

568
00:27:27,360 --> 00:27:28,650
cultivating basic interests.

569
00:27:28,650 --> 00:27:29,520
These professional skills

570
00:27:29,520 --> 00:27:31,780
are all acquired through further study.

571
00:27:33,080 --> 00:27:35,250
I'm going to do fieldwork in the future.

572
00:27:35,250 --> 00:27:37,240
There are technicians to
draw these things.

573
00:27:37,240 --> 00:27:39,370
If you can accept that
your drawing skills are not

574
00:27:39,370 --> 00:27:41,050
as good as the technicians' in the field,

575
00:27:41,050 --> 00:27:41,850
just go ahead.

576
00:27:44,560 --> 00:27:45,360
That's right.

577
00:27:45,820 --> 00:27:46,930
Let me learn about

578
00:27:47,040 --> 00:27:49,800
what level a top talent from
Peking University is really at.

579
00:27:49,800 --> 00:27:50,330
Alright.

580
00:27:50,650 --> 00:27:52,800
Since you have insights,
let's discuss. Come on.

581
00:27:52,800 --> 00:27:53,390
Bring it on.

582
00:27:53,390 --> 00:27:54,860
I wouldn't dare.

583
00:28:02,040 --> 00:28:02,570
Alright.

584
00:28:06,160 --> 00:28:07,490
It looks quite similar.

585
00:28:07,840 --> 00:28:10,410
But in terms of archaeology, is it enough
to just capture the likeness?

586
00:28:10,410 --> 00:28:11,870
I've noticed that you've
been here for just a short time.

587
00:28:11,870 --> 00:28:13,360
Let me briefly summarize

588
00:28:13,360 --> 00:28:15,760
the basics that Mr. Zan
usually teaches us.

589
00:28:16,490 --> 00:28:17,550
Listen carefully.

590
00:28:17,840 --> 00:28:18,970
Put on your glasses.

591
00:28:24,250 --> 00:28:25,170
Look at

592
00:28:25,520 --> 00:28:28,170
Mr. Zhang's drawing of Jiang Tribe.

593
00:28:28,690 --> 00:28:31,750
That's a very standard archaeological illustration.

594
00:28:32,280 --> 00:28:33,210
It's primitive,

595
00:28:33,410 --> 00:28:34,340
full of vitality

596
00:28:34,800 --> 00:28:35,800
and interesting.

597
00:28:35,890 --> 00:28:38,350
Look. What features does
your drawing have?

598
00:28:38,360 --> 00:28:40,360
It looks as cold as winter.

599
00:28:40,450 --> 00:28:41,880
Mr. Zhang, whom you've mentioned,

600
00:28:41,880 --> 00:28:44,040
is the pioneer of archaeological
illustrations in China.

601
00:28:44,040 --> 00:28:45,500
How can I compare with him?

602
00:28:49,090 --> 00:28:50,220
Why did you stand up?

603
00:28:50,890 --> 00:28:51,560
We're in class.

604
00:28:51,560 --> 00:28:53,220
Why did you stand up? Sit down!

605
00:28:53,440 --> 00:28:55,370
If you can't draw well, just learn.

606
00:28:55,760 --> 00:28:56,600
If you can't draw well in a month,

607
00:28:56,600 --> 00:28:57,760
can't you draw for two months?

608
00:28:57,760 --> 00:29:00,600
If you can't draw well
in two months, draw for a year.

609
00:29:00,600 --> 00:29:02,260
Keep drawing until it's good.

610
00:29:07,930 --> 00:29:08,560
Mr. Zan.

611
00:29:08,890 --> 00:29:10,220
I have something to say.

612
00:29:10,690 --> 00:29:11,800
Luo Qing, Shilin.

613
00:29:12,210 --> 00:29:13,210
Pack your things.

614
00:29:13,410 --> 00:29:14,690
Come with me on a mission.

615
00:29:14,690 --> 00:29:16,010
Mr. Zan, what mission is it?

616
00:29:16,010 --> 00:29:18,450
A robbed Tang-Dynasty tomb that's not far
from Yangling has been discovered.

617
00:29:16,150 --> 00:29:18,350
[Zan Maochang, Professor of
Qinbei University]

618
00:29:18,570 --> 00:29:20,280
The Cultural Heritage Bureau requires us

619
00:29:20,280 --> 00:29:22,600
to conduct emergency excavations
as soon as possible.

620
00:29:22,600 --> 00:29:25,000
Alright. Let's pack up
and set off quickly.

621
00:29:25,740 --> 00:29:26,800
What are you doing?

622
00:29:32,930 --> 00:29:33,970
This drawing

623
00:29:34,250 --> 00:29:35,580
not only lakcs artistry

624
00:29:36,160 --> 00:29:39,490
but also doesn't meet the most
basic scientific standards.

625
00:29:39,490 --> 00:29:41,550
Alright. Stay here and keep drawing.

626
00:29:41,550 --> 00:29:43,100
If you can't draw well
in a month, draw for two months.

627
00:29:43,100 --> 00:29:44,690
If you can't draw well
in two months, draw for a year.

628
00:29:44,690 --> 00:29:46,010
Keep drawing until it's good.

629
00:29:46,010 --> 00:29:47,930
Luo Qing has only
been here for half a month.

630
00:29:47,930 --> 00:29:49,360
Why can she go and I can't?

631
00:29:49,440 --> 00:29:50,630
Because she draws better than you.

632
00:29:50,630 --> 00:29:51,860
But I've been drawing carefully, too.

633
00:29:51,860 --> 00:29:53,490
Look at these calluses on my hands.

634
00:29:53,490 --> 00:29:55,140
They can prove my hard work.

635
00:29:55,170 --> 00:29:57,930
Effort without diligence is wasted effort.

636
00:29:57,950 --> 00:29:59,450
Mr. Zan, do you have a problem with me?

637
00:29:59,450 --> 00:30:00,980
I do have a problem with you.

638
00:30:01,430 --> 00:30:02,360
Just look at it.

639
00:30:02,510 --> 00:30:04,920
After eight months, this is what
you've accomplished?

640
00:30:04,920 --> 00:30:07,580
What have you been
thinking about all this time?

641
00:30:08,250 --> 00:30:10,180
Of course I have a problem with you.

642
00:30:23,210 --> 00:30:23,840
Xinzhi?

643
00:30:24,800 --> 00:30:25,730
Why are you here?

644
00:30:25,930 --> 00:30:27,130
Come on. Give it to me.

645
00:30:28,120 --> 00:30:29,980
Why didn't you tell me in advance?

646
00:30:30,910 --> 00:30:32,440
You're really so annoying.

647
00:30:33,420 --> 00:30:35,750
Now you're even setting your sights on me.

648
00:30:36,110 --> 00:30:37,150
What's wrong?

649
00:30:38,560 --> 00:30:38,840
I...

650
00:30:43,290 --> 00:30:45,450
So you're talking about
the Tang Dynasty tomb?

651
00:30:45,450 --> 00:30:47,080
You're an expert in Qin and Han Dynasties.

652
00:30:47,080 --> 00:30:49,940
But you're reaching into my Sui and Tang territory.

653
00:30:51,010 --> 00:30:51,760
Xinzhi.

654
00:30:52,770 --> 00:30:56,230
How can you say this Tang Dynasty tomb
has nothing to do with me?

655
00:30:56,360 --> 00:30:57,820
Think about its location.

656
00:30:58,120 --> 00:30:59,920
It's very close to our Yangling.

657
00:31:00,040 --> 00:31:01,570
Its excavation data will be

658
00:31:01,570 --> 00:31:03,360
very helpful for our research into

659
00:31:03,360 --> 00:31:05,250
the historical geographic

660
00:31:06,210 --> 00:31:07,470
location of Yangling.

661
00:31:07,520 --> 00:31:08,970
Zan Maochang.

662
00:31:09,730 --> 00:31:11,860
You can fool outsiders with that talk.

663
00:31:12,120 --> 00:31:14,560
I know your little scheme.

664
00:31:15,040 --> 00:31:17,120
Your Yangling research is short of funds,

665
00:31:17,120 --> 00:31:18,930
so you've taken on
the emergency excavations

666
00:31:18,930 --> 00:31:19,970
of the Tang Dynasty tomb.

667
00:31:19,970 --> 00:31:21,630
The money issue is solved now.

668
00:31:21,650 --> 00:31:22,080
Right?

669
00:31:27,270 --> 00:31:29,750
N-Nothing can be kept from you.

670
00:31:32,800 --> 00:31:34,260
Xinzhi, here's the thing.

671
00:31:34,320 --> 00:31:35,850
Just do me a favor this time.

672
00:31:36,650 --> 00:31:38,010
Look, this excavation has been

673
00:31:38,010 --> 00:31:39,470
initiated by your provincial institute.

674
00:31:39,470 --> 00:31:42,540
You'll be the team leader.
It's such a great opportunity.

675
00:31:42,540 --> 00:31:44,010
Just let my students and me

676
00:31:44,320 --> 00:31:45,490
be your assistants.

677
00:31:46,650 --> 00:31:48,600
You'll make decisions on vital matters.

678
00:31:48,600 --> 00:31:50,800
I'll help you with the trivial matters.

679
00:31:50,840 --> 00:31:52,770
I'll listen to you. How about that?

680
00:31:57,730 --> 00:31:58,730
Mr. Mu, you're back.

681
00:31:58,730 --> 00:31:59,260
I'm back.

682
00:32:17,320 --> 00:32:18,040
I'm back.

683
00:32:18,650 --> 00:32:19,490
You're back.

684
00:32:20,490 --> 00:32:21,600
Eat first.

685
00:32:21,690 --> 00:32:23,020
The food is on the stove.

686
00:32:23,520 --> 00:32:24,050
No hurry.

687
00:32:24,890 --> 00:32:26,020
The herbs are ready.

688
00:32:26,120 --> 00:32:27,850
I'll decoct them for you first.

689
00:32:42,840 --> 00:32:45,730
My damned illness is so annoying.

690
00:32:46,450 --> 00:32:47,180
Next year...

691
00:32:47,930 --> 00:32:50,130
Next year, we'll move to a bigger house.

692
00:32:50,280 --> 00:32:51,940
We'll find one with a balcony.

693
00:32:52,080 --> 00:32:53,610
You can sunbathe every day.

694
00:32:55,240 --> 00:32:57,070
How can we afford to move?

695
00:32:57,170 --> 00:32:58,250
Don't say that.

696
00:32:59,120 --> 00:33:01,210
If others can get rich, so can we.

697
00:33:03,450 --> 00:33:04,800
Where did you go today?

698
00:33:05,590 --> 00:33:06,790
Where else could I go?

699
00:33:07,040 --> 00:33:08,770
I was selling goods at my stall.

700
00:33:10,080 --> 00:33:11,140
You're lying to me.

701
00:33:12,650 --> 00:33:16,310
I looked for you in the South Market
at noon, but you weren't there.

702
00:33:16,800 --> 00:33:17,890
At noon?

703
00:33:18,930 --> 00:33:19,600
At noon,

704
00:33:20,690 --> 00:33:22,350
I went away to buy this for you.

705
00:33:23,600 --> 00:33:24,120
Look.

706
00:33:27,080 --> 00:33:29,010
If you need anything in the future,

707
00:33:29,360 --> 00:33:31,340
just call me directly.

708
00:33:38,320 --> 00:33:39,850
Where did you get the money?

709
00:33:39,890 --> 00:33:40,690
I had savings.

710
00:33:46,520 --> 00:33:47,890
Can you do me a favor?

711
00:33:48,970 --> 00:33:50,040
There's something under the bed.

712
00:33:50,040 --> 00:33:51,380
Can you take it out for me?

713
00:33:51,380 --> 00:33:52,580
What is it?

714
00:33:58,650 --> 00:34:01,850
How do you explain the pottery
figurines in the suitcase?

715
00:34:02,210 --> 00:34:05,120
You must have robbed the grave
with Sheng and the others.

716
00:34:05,120 --> 00:34:06,980
I bought those pottery figurines

717
00:34:07,450 --> 00:34:08,770
from the countryside.

718
00:34:09,010 --> 00:34:10,239
You're still lying to me.

719
00:34:10,239 --> 00:34:11,409
I'm not lying to you.

720
00:34:12,719 --> 00:34:13,600
Because of my damned illness,

721
00:34:13,600 --> 00:34:16,489
all our family incomes have
been used on my medicine.

722
00:34:16,489 --> 00:34:18,489
Where could you get money to buy goods?

723
00:34:18,489 --> 00:34:19,770
Where could you get money
to buy me a mobile phone

724
00:34:19,770 --> 00:34:20,900
and all those herbs?

725
00:34:22,719 --> 00:34:24,520
We can't do bad things like that.

726
00:34:25,010 --> 00:34:27,469
It will come back to haunt us sooner or later.

727
00:34:28,040 --> 00:34:29,770
I can't control Sheng anymore.

728
00:34:30,719 --> 00:34:31,600
Just let him be.

729
00:34:32,199 --> 00:34:33,489
But I can't watch you

730
00:34:33,489 --> 00:34:35,219
stray from the righteous path.

731
00:34:36,199 --> 00:34:37,120
Shulan.

732
00:34:38,159 --> 00:34:39,520
Look.

733
00:34:39,850 --> 00:34:42,449
Why did you start crying
while we were talking?

734
00:34:43,850 --> 00:34:44,710
Think about it.

735
00:34:45,449 --> 00:34:47,050
What kind of person is Sheng?

736
00:34:47,520 --> 00:34:49,120
He's mindful of every penny.

737
00:34:50,290 --> 00:34:51,820
Would he let me participate

738
00:34:52,080 --> 00:34:53,679
in the profitable business?

739
00:34:54,290 --> 00:34:54,889
Besides,

740
00:34:55,120 --> 00:34:56,810
I can't do laborious work.

741
00:34:56,929 --> 00:34:57,720
I can be neither a grave digger

742
00:34:57,720 --> 00:34:59,180
nor an on-site commander.

743
00:34:59,770 --> 00:35:02,370
I've just had a bit of luck recently.

744
00:35:03,200 --> 00:35:06,490
My friend from the countryside
was willing to give me goods on credit

745
00:35:06,490 --> 00:35:08,290
so that I could earn some profit.

746
00:35:12,290 --> 00:35:13,550
You're not lying to me?

747
00:35:13,640 --> 00:35:14,840
How would I lie to you?

748
00:35:17,080 --> 00:35:19,490
You're annoying. I was so scared.

749
00:35:19,810 --> 00:35:21,160
Don't be scared.

750
00:35:22,290 --> 00:35:24,890
Look at the mobile phone.
Come on. Open the box.

751
00:35:27,240 --> 00:35:27,770
Look.

752
00:35:28,680 --> 00:35:29,610
It's a new model.

753
00:35:32,890 --> 00:35:33,420
Not much.

754
00:35:33,770 --> 00:35:34,500
10,000 yuan.

755
00:35:34,890 --> 00:35:36,680
It's up to you how much you'll give

756
00:35:36,680 --> 00:35:37,940
to your grave diggers.

757
00:35:46,240 --> 00:35:47,850
Bro, I've made up my mind.

758
00:35:48,520 --> 00:35:50,520
I won't do anything else from now on.

759
00:35:51,370 --> 00:35:52,630
I'll just work for you.

760
00:35:52,680 --> 00:35:54,120
I'll do whatever you say.

761
00:35:54,410 --> 00:35:56,010
No rush. Take it slow.

762
00:35:56,520 --> 00:35:58,240
Our good days are yet to come.

763
00:36:00,720 --> 00:36:01,970
When we were at the watch factory,

764
00:36:01,970 --> 00:36:04,640
I knew you would accomplish great things

765
00:36:04,940 --> 00:36:06,740
and would be someone important.

766
00:36:08,490 --> 00:36:09,420
In your opinion,

767
00:36:10,010 --> 00:36:11,870
what kind of person is important?

768
00:36:12,640 --> 00:36:13,850
Well, people like

769
00:36:14,160 --> 00:36:16,600
the emperors of Qin, Han, Tang and Song Dynasties.

770
00:36:16,600 --> 00:36:17,130
Alright.

771
00:36:18,120 --> 00:36:20,370
From now on, as for the treasures
used by emperors and ministers,

772
00:36:20,370 --> 00:36:21,970
we'll take whatever we want.

773
00:36:22,040 --> 00:36:22,720
Okay.

774
00:36:25,200 --> 00:36:27,130
Come on. Let me drink a toast to you.

775
00:36:27,720 --> 00:36:28,180
Cheers.

776
00:36:31,290 --> 00:36:36,280
[November, 2002]

777
00:36:45,680 --> 00:36:47,460
Thanks for your hard work, Captain Qi.

778
00:36:47,460 --> 00:36:50,390
Your trip to Suizhou in the south
was quite fruitful.

779
00:36:50,940 --> 00:36:54,790
[Qi Dacang, Captain of Relics Inspection
Team of Municipal Public Security Bureau]

780
00:36:51,120 --> 00:36:54,010
I'm ashamed. We only retrieved
34 black pottery figurines.

781
00:36:54,010 --> 00:36:55,410
The other ones were all lost.

782
00:36:55,410 --> 00:36:57,140
You've already done your best.

783
00:36:58,720 --> 00:37:00,650
I know everyone is concerned about

784
00:37:01,290 --> 00:37:03,240
the current state of the six withdrawn

785
00:37:03,240 --> 00:37:06,500
black pottery figurines from
the Winthrop Auction House.

786
00:37:07,240 --> 00:37:09,640
We've just received news from the embassy.

787
00:37:09,680 --> 00:37:12,770
The foreign customs have
detained these cultural relics.

788
00:37:12,770 --> 00:37:13,770
The reason is that

789
00:37:14,290 --> 00:37:16,490
the evidence we provided is too simple.

790
00:37:16,930 --> 00:37:19,160
They've raised more questions.

791
00:37:19,680 --> 00:37:20,410
For example,

792
00:37:20,890 --> 00:37:21,850
can we specify

793
00:37:22,890 --> 00:37:23,520
how many

794
00:37:24,040 --> 00:37:26,370
pottery figurines there were in the tomb?

795
00:37:26,600 --> 00:37:27,330
In addition,

796
00:37:28,410 --> 00:37:29,010
what else

797
00:37:30,410 --> 00:37:31,810
was in the tomb?

798
00:37:32,370 --> 00:37:33,010
Right now, we don't

799
00:37:33,010 --> 00:37:34,940
even know where the looting pit is.

800
00:37:36,810 --> 00:37:38,720
How could we know
what it's like inside the tomb?

801
00:37:38,720 --> 00:37:39,520
Ultimately,

802
00:37:40,010 --> 00:37:43,370
we need to find the looting pit where
the black pottery figurines were unearthed

803
00:37:43,370 --> 00:37:44,310
and prove that

804
00:37:44,560 --> 00:37:47,070
the black pottery figurines are indeed from that looting pit.

805
00:37:47,070 --> 00:37:49,540
[Zhao Feng, Deputy Chief of
Municipal Public Security Bureau]

806
00:37:48,160 --> 00:37:48,820
Chief Zhao.

807
00:37:49,520 --> 00:37:52,200
Whether we can retrieve these six black pottery figurines

808
00:37:52,200 --> 00:37:54,400
depends on whether our police officers

809
00:37:54,770 --> 00:37:56,120
can solve this case.

810
00:37:56,720 --> 00:37:57,850
What's the time limit?

